               Successfully started the instance: yml-i-sj01
               instance Location: /export/glassfish3/glassfish/nodes/sj01/yml-i-sj01
               Log File: /export/glassfish3/glassfish/nodes/sj01/yml-i-sj01/logs/server.log
               Admin Port: 24849
